{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-product","blocks":{"title":{"type":"title","settings":{}},"4882410d-eb44-4444-9258-6624e44f6a87":{"type":"subtitle","settings":{"pro-subtitle":"<strong>UNISEX PERFUME<\/strong>"}},"text_EFDcjF":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"“My wife absolutely loves this scent on me, It’s become my signature scent. Ordered a bottle for her as well” - <strong>Robert M.<\/strong>","text_style":"body"}},"0018d287-cdf5-4517-af5c-6a7840052b0a":{"type":"price","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"af9f4454-06eb-434c-86ea-059b201ecec6":{"type":"description","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"variant_picker":{"type":"variant_picker","settings":{"picker_type":"button"}},"buy_buttons":{"type":"buy_buttons","settings":{"shipping-txt":"<strong>2~3 Day Shipping from London, UK🇬🇧<\/strong>","show_dynamic_checkout":false,"show_gift_card_recipient":true}},"a134f827-c44e-4834-abbb-dea857d93816":{"type":"icon-with-text","settings":{"layout":"horizontal","icon_1":"truck","heading_1":"Shipped from U.K","icon_2":"return","heading_2":"Money Back Gurantee","icon_3":"heart","heading_3":"Loved by 10K+"}},"29f02082-10d7-4a2d-ad99-f56582cc1504":{"type":"collapsible_tab","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Where is it made?","icon":"question_mark","content":"<p><strong>Using Nano-Crystalline technology, <\/strong>Bleame™ Crystal Hair Eraser allows the hair to clump and break from the surface when rubbed gently on the skin. This process also helps exfoliate, revealing baby smooth skin after use 💜<\/p>","page":""}},"e31ec655-753c-48fd-80e7-8acaf40092f7":{"type":"instruction_tab","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Instructions","icon":"star","content":"<h3>Prep Your Skin<\/h3><p>Exfoliate your skin no less than 24 hours before use. If you have sensitive skin, exfoliate no less than 48 hours before use.<\/p><h3>Patch Test for Sensitivity<\/h3><p>Conduct a <a href=\"https:\/\/help.bleame.com\/en-US\/how-to-do-a-patch-test-before-using-bleame-crystal-hair-eraser-254672\"><strong>patch test<\/strong><\/a> on a small area of each leg: one with damp skin and the other with dry skin. Test with moisture barriers like hypoallergenic moisturizer or cream. Allow it to fully absorb before using your Eraser. For added comfort, test with a protective layer of shaving gel or cream.<\/p><h3>Get to action<\/h3><p>After a successful patch test, treat your desired areas using the method and technique that felt most comfortable during testing. Start with gentle, circular motions and light pressure. Adjust your technique as needed, avoiding excessive pressure that may cause irritation. Take breaks between passes and use shorter strokes to minimize friction and heat.<\/p><h3>Aftercare for Soothing Relief<\/h3><p>Rinse the treated area with cool water and gently pat it dry, avoiding rubbing. Apply a fragrance-free, hypoallergenic moisturizer. For an extra relief, use a cold compress for 10-15 minutes.<\/p><h3>Caring for Your Eraser<\/h3><p>After each use, rinse your Crystal Hair Eraser under running water to remove hair and exfoliated skin. Store the eraser in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight and humidity.<br\/>Important Note: If you experience any discomfort or irritation during or after use, discontinue use immediately. <a href=\"https:\/\/help.bleame.com\/en-US\/how-to-effectively-use-the-bleame-crystal-hair-eraser-254714\"><strong>Visit our Help Center for more information.<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","page":""}},"137bee7a-dd9c-415e-ac1c-7c29ab2fd653":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Shipping","icon":"truck","content":"<p>We are based in Dubai however we have a warehouse in London, hence shipments all over<strong> UK take only 2-3 days and cost £5. <\/strong><\/p>","page":""}},"55879359-71f2-45bb-9e58-3c0de78c7375":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Return & Refund Policy","icon":"return","content":"<p><strong>1.1 Return Due To Change Of Mind<\/strong><\/p><p>A-scent will happily accept returns due to change of mind as long as a request to return is received by us within 72 hours of receipt of item. <\/p><p>Once approved, refunds will be processed to their original payment method. We will notify you once this has been completed through email.<\/p><p>Ascent will refund the value of the goods returned but will NOT refund the value of any shipping paid.<\/p><p><strong>1.2 Cancellations<\/strong><\/p><p>If you change your mind before a tracking numbers has been generated, we are able to accept cancellations at any time before the order has been dispatched. If an order has already been dispatched, please refer to our refund policy.<\/p>","page":""}},"bcec75a1-c328-4842-87bf-7cc6efbe88f2":{"type":"logo-list","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p>10,000+ Oud Implosion Lovers<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["title","4882410d-eb44-4444-9258-6624e44f6a87","text_EFDcjF","0018d287-cdf5-4517-af5c-6a7840052b0a","af9f4454-06eb-434c-86ea-059b201ecec6","variant_picker","buy_buttons","a134f827-c44e-4834-abbb-dea857d93816","29f02082-10d7-4a2d-ad99-f56582cc1504","e31ec655-753c-48fd-80e7-8acaf40092f7","137bee7a-dd9c-415e-ac1c-7c29ab2fd653","55879359-71f2-45bb-9e58-3c0de78c7375","bcec75a1-c328-4842-87bf-7cc6efbe88f2"],"settings":{"enable_sticky_info":true,"media_size":"medium","constrain_to_viewport":true,"media_fit":"cover","gallery_layout":"thumbnail_slider","media_position":"left","image_zoom":"none","mobile_thumbnails":"hide","hide_variants":false,"enable_video_looping":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":12}},"4536657b-07aa-4787-922f-be0de52afe9c":{"type":"image-with-text-2","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Look At How Others Are Loving Their Bleame","text":"<p>These women are actual Bleame customers that have seen results with consistent use of Bleame's Gua Sha Facial Set!<\/p>","rev-text":"Rated 4.9\/5 by 175,000+ Happy Customers","btn-txt":"Claim Offer","btn-link":"#","btn-bg-color":"#7069bc","btn-txt-color":"#ffffff"}},"image_banner_TmDkKP":{"type":"image-banner","blocks":{"heading_XMjNjf":{"t